hwa (command) [args]

 convert:
  Converts a supported package to a Windows Appx package. I.e.:
   hwa crxtoappx ./myapp.crx

 deploy:
  Registers and launches an AppxManifest or URL. I.e.:
   hwa deploy http://dev.windows.com
   hwa deploy path-to-AppxManifest.xml

 restart:
  Starts or restarts the previous Appx deployed using this tool.
 
 
 Remote Commands
 The following commands are only usable when using this tool to connect to an HWA-Server.
 
 clearsession:
  Clears the session file, causing the next deploy to re-provision a server.
 
 exit:
  Disconnects the provisioned HWA-Server.